com.yworks.yfiles.geometry

Interface IMutableSize

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISize
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IMutableOrientedRectangle, IMutableRectangle
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MutableRectangle, MutableSize, OrientedRectangle

    public interface IMutableSize
extends ISize
    Interface for a mutable size in 2D coordinate space with double precision width and height.

    This interface provides read and write access to the size. It extends the read only interface ISize.

    See Also:
    ISize, MutableSize
